data.description: Sold As Is - This is a 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom property located in Killeen that offers great potential for investors. With over 2100 sqft of space, this property has a lot of room for increasing its resale value. However, the property needs some attention as the pool in the backyard requires servicing or may need to be filled in. The property is situated just minutes away from Fort Cavazos and Texas A&M, making it ideal for a profitable fix-and-flip project or a secure and reliable buy and hold investment.
